{"tid":284870,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《 黑豹 》六大黑人演員飾演六大新角色","createTime":"2017-06-15T09:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T15:47:25.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62c5fee739d88c146ccc2289c40d8f230ce4ed9f","tid":284870,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:48:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://blog.hkmovie6.com/電影熱話/黑豹/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.hkmovie6.com%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F%E9%BB%91%E8%B1%B9%2F&d=XPfWdIJ1qqwkHC814Ko3JQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5e9ac870\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.hkmovie6.com/電影熱話/黑豹/</a><br />\n<br />\nMarvel 超級英雄電影《 黑豹 》在日前終於推出了首波預告片。以虛構非洲國家瓦干達為故事舞台，作為 MCU 第一齣以黑人角色為首的電影《 黑豹 》雲集多位黑人演員精英。除了已經與大家率先於《 美國隊長3：英雄內戰 》見過面，由&nbsp;查特域克保斯曼&nbsp;飾演的主角黑豹 T&rsquo;Challa 之外，還有以下六大新角色：<br />\n<br />\nErik Killmonger<br />\n神奇4俠》、《洛奇外傳 &mdash; 王者之後》米高B佐敦 飾演&nbsp;N&rsquo;Jadaka<br />\n<br />\n本名為 N&rsquo;Jadaka，於漫畫中因被流放而對瓦干達產生復仇之心，前往紐約後改名為&nbsp;Erik Killmonger，是個格鬥實力與黑豹相若的大反派。<br />\n<br />\nNakia<br />\n<br />\n《被奪走的12年》奧斯卡最佳女配角&nbsp;雷碧達尼安高 飾演&nbsp;Nakia<br />\n<br />\n非常傾慕黑豹的女性，因闖禍而不能再侍奉黑豹，後被黑豹的敵人殺死，但被 Erik Killmonger 以魔法復活後向瓦干達展開復仇。在今次電影中仍然為黑豹的保鏢。"},{"pid":"722c1c3a551fa75cd8f313d56166da217806e989","tid":284870,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"Okoye<br />\n<br />\n《行屍》人氣女星&nbsp;Danai Gurira 飾演&nbsp;Okoye<br />\n<br />\n與好姊妹 Nakia 同被選中成為守護黑豹的女性，但並未像 Nakia 一樣渴望成為瓦干達王后，選擇成為侍衛長，全力協助黑豹。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nW&rsquo;Kabi<br />\n<br />\n《訪．嚇》人氣男星 丹尼爾卡魯亞 飾演&nbsp;W&rsquo;Kabi<br />\n<br />\n黑豹的好兄弟兼副手，右手裝上藏有大殺傷力武器的機械手臂。<br />\n<br />\nZuri<br />\n<br />\n《最後的蘇格蘭王》奧斯卡金像影帝&nbsp;科力士韋德加 飾演 Zuri<br />\n<br />\n前任瓦干達國王的護衛，並與雷神份屬友好，是瓦干達的戰鬥好手。於電影一開始設定為瓦干達的長老。"},{"pid":"5737ed533d5c8eff5f09b8ce583c34c6a43f554c","tid":284870,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:50:28.000Z","msg":"Man Ape<br />\n<br />\n《摩登家庭》新晉男星 Winston Duke 飾演M&rsquo;Baku<br />\n<br />\n原名為&nbsp;M&rsquo;Baku，本來是實力僅次於黑豹的瓦干達戰士，但因渴求謀朝篡位，吞食白猿肉以及浸浴於白猿血而獲得神秘力量成為超級壞蛋 Man Ape。電影設定為瓦干達敵對部落的領導人。<br />\n<br />\nLetitia Wright 飾演&nbsp;Shuri<br />\n<br />\n黑豹的父王 T&rsquo;Chaka、母后 Ramonda 和王妹 Shuri 都會現身。已故的 T&rsquo;Chaka 應該會連同年輕版本的黑豹、Erik Killmonger 出現於回憶片段，而於《英雄內戰》中初次登場的黑豹黑面女保鏢 Ayo 亦會再度現身。"},{"pid":"81de8ec2bf107a95b5bf36feb2623cd682e34f7c","tid":284870,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"呢啲蹺口名似係屬於Star Wars 人物多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e5e29ad096d4e6bf35274a586406c654a5169e","tid":284870,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:58:25.000Z","msg":"W&rsquo;Kabi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaa80a8b5a64acc872c1727d2a7f2110b600e2f","tid":284870,"uid":3577,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"唔睇了 , 我怕黑"},{"pid":"3847c7f0653026b03709c4c1773893dea49e32eb","tid":284870,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:00:56.000Z","msg":"nigga"},{"pid":"62a9771e7b690f268d8efc31cf24ae2e64fc64ec","tid":284870,"uid":5460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"尼架俠"},{"pid":"c683c63a6a2e19f9d96e3e966a3114d89e4f70a3","tid":284870,"uid":3405,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"一張相都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bac160d82b98b6a330f2fcf9abb6e541624ef6","tid":284870,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d2acf2283f7fbc8bc84f78bfe6786941d2f98fb","tid":284870,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Man Ape<br />\n<br />\n《摩登家庭》新晉男星 Winston Duke 飾演M&rsquo;Baku<br />\n<br />\n原名為&nbsp;M&rsquo;Baku，本來是實力僅次於黑豹的瓦干達戰士，但因渴求謀朝篡位，吞食白猿肉以及浸浴於白猿血而獲得神秘力量成為超級壞蛋 Man Ape。電影設定為瓦干達敵對部落的領導人。<br />\n<br />\nLetitia Wright 飾演&nbsp;Shuri<br />\n<br />\n黑豹的父王 T&rsquo;Chaka、母后 Ramonda 和王妹 Shuri 都會現身。已故的 T&rsquo;Chaka 應該會連同年輕版本的黑豹、Erik Killmonger 出現於回憶片段，而於《英雄內戰》中初次登場的黑豹黑面女保鏢 Ayo 亦會再度現身。</blockquote><br />\n黑得濟睇唔到d相"},{"pid":"9d4e1d2c5ef999e749ebb4da4209c57a0791bc6b","tid":284870,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一張相都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完相都分唔清啲人"},{"pid":"724afd2ef8ca2cf5e4b35d56097b46a303f3e3dd","tid":284870,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"仲以為係Jamie Foxx，Denzel Washington，Morgan Freeman嗰啲添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dd1a4ac6055424bbd29ad912e53158ddc9129a","tid":284870,"uid":35766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔睇了 , 我怕黑</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c364280a8a6332c64ef16fa907d1a0efbb6f8f","tid":284870,"uid":8088,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:18:25.000Z","msg":"中譯：力架奇俠/黑炮大奔州"},{"pid":"ff074ef7cb6c808fa9b96de3f669ce2502490227","tid":284870,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"其實黑豹成身都係 CA個盾果種質地<br />\n照計冇人打到佢喎 <br />\n用電搞到佢觸電就另計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5962461b3922fd2c166f81c5004351dda36f2df0","tid":284870,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實黑豹成身都係 CA個盾果種質地<br />\n照計冇人打到佢喎 <br />\n用電搞到佢觸電就另計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似有少少唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl